--- Requires Installation:
* ncursesw (development library)
* pkg-config
* automake
* autoconf
* binutils
* ncurses
* glibc
* make
* gcc

--- Make sure charset is set to UTF-8
run the 'locale' command

--- Spell
autoreconf -iv && ./configure && sudo make install

--- File Structure
/usr/local/bin/typp
/usr/local/share/typp/
/usr/local/share/typp/eng.typp
/usr/local/share/typp/rus.typp
/usr/local/man/man6/typp.6

--- Platform
The project was tested only on Linux Manjaro Xfce 5.10.42-1-MANJARO x86_64
